  <brief_title>Urinary Catheter Exchange on Admission of Septic Elderly With Permanent Catheter Before Initiation of Antibiotics</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Shaare Zedek Medical Center</agency>
